column5: Looking to stock up and was wondering if anyone has ever purchased from this online retailer in Canada?  Thanks in advance
Funny. I seen a truck in Barrie this week with that site on his back window. Maybe he was sponsored by them, as he was a member of the Barrie Bassmasters.
I've never dealt with them but I'm not impressed at all.
I've never dealt with them but I'm not impressed at all.   me neither, plus the cost of shipping would negate any 'savings'.  better off going to the local shop
